# Implementation Plan: Workspace Stabilization & Protocol Sync

This plan addresses the technical debt identified in the Project Audit, focusing on workspace organization and protocol alignment.

## Proposed Changes

### [Workspace Organization]
Cleanup of the root directory to reduce cognitive load and version fragmentation.

#### [MOVE] [heart_pipeline_v10_*.py](file:///home/kizabgd/Desktop/Istrazivanje/)
- Move all `heart_pipeline_v10_[1-13]*.py` files to `.legacy/heart_versions/`.
- Keep [heart_pipeline_v10_14_sota.py](file:///home/kizabgd/Desktop/Istrazivanje/heart_pipeline_v10_14_sota.py) in the root (current entrypoint).

#### [MOVE] [.csv & .log files](file:///home/kizabgd/Desktop/Istrazivanje/)
- Move loose CSV files (e.g., `submission_*.csv`, [reference.csv](file:///home/kizabgd/Desktop/Istrazivanje/reference.csv)) to `data_hub/archive/`.
- Move loose log files (e.g., [api_prod_test.log](file:///home/kizabgd/Desktop/Istrazivanje/api_prod_test.log), [dashboard.log](file:///home/kizabgd/Desktop/Istrazivanje/dashboard.log)) to `logs/archive/`.

