## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- **Makefile Smoke Test**:
    ```bash
    make help
    ```
- **Manifest Validation**:
    - Verify [manifest.json](file:///home/kizabgd/Desktop/Istrazivanje/manifest.json) matches [trinity_config.json](file:///home/kizabgd/Desktop/Istrazivanje/trinity_config.json) version logic.
- **Protocol Smoke Test**:
