    ```

### Manual Verification
- Verify that the root directory is significantly less cluttered.
- Confirm that [heart_pipeline_v10_14_sota.py](file:///home/kizabgd/Desktop/Istrazivanje/heart_pipeline_v10_14_sota.py) still runs correctly after file moves (path check for [train.csv](file:///home/kizabgd/Desktop/Istrazivanje/train.csv) and [test.csv](file:///home/kizabgd/Desktop/Istrazivanje/test.csv)).
